OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,FThe community in Calne is being asked
OL,7,Fto provide their views on the
OL,8,Fpersistent odour issue and how
OL,9,Fauthorities are tackling the problem.
OL,11,FThe smell has previously been linked
OL,12,Fto escaping gas from the Lower Compton
OL,13,Flandfill site, operated by Hills Waste
OL,14,FSolutions.
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency (EA) is hosting
OL,17,Fa community drop-in event on 21 July,
OL,18,Fwith the UK Health Security Agency
OL,19,F(UKHSA) and Wiltshire Council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
