OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,FThe UKHSA has published a public
OL,7,Fhealth risk assessment using data
OL,8,Fcollected by the Environment Agency's
OL,9,FMobile Monitoring Facility in the
OL,10,FCalne community.
OL,12,FLocals will be able to talk about the
OL,13,Ffindings of the assessment with those
OL,14,Finvolved in trying to tackle the
OL,15,Fproblem.
OL,17,FThe data given by the Environment
OL,18,FAgency shows there is a source of
OL,19,Fhydrogen sulphide and methane in the
OL,20,Fdirection of the Lower Compton
OL,21,FLandfill.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,FThe EA say this "confirms the findings
OL,7,Fof our inspections and off-site odour
OL,8,Fassessments, and supports the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency's regulatory
OL,10,Fdecisions, including telling the
OL,11,Foperator Hills to bring capping works
OL,12,Fforward and change the ways they
OL,13,Fmanage odour".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
