CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,FResidents hoped the long-running
OL,7,Fproblem had been resolved when the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency intervened in June
OL,9,F2025, serving Hills with an
OL,10,Fenforcement notice ordering the
OL,11,Fcompany to complete a programme of
OL,12,Flandfill capping designed to trap
OL,13,Fescaping gas and reduce odours.
OL,15,FBen Shayler, Area Environment Manager
OL,16,Fsaid: "This drop in event will give
OL,17,Fresidents the opportunity to
OL,18,Funderstand the work we are doing to
OL,19,Fregulate Hills, and ask questions of
OL,20,Fthe agencies involved.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,F"We have taken extensive action to
OL,7,Frequire Hills to address the source of
OL,8,Fthe odour, and these works are now
OL,9,Fnearing completion.
OL,11,F"We will continue to regulate the site
OL,12,Fclosely and monitor to ensure the
OL,13,Fworks have been effective."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
