PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,FLucy McCann, Consultant in Health
OL,7,FProtection at UKHSA South West, said:
OL,8,F"UKHSA has reviewed the Environment
OL,9,FAgency's public health risk assessment
OL,10,Fand provided an independent public
OL,11,Fhealth risk assessment. While there is
OL,12,Fno evidence of a toxicological risk,
OL,13,Fthere is strong evidence of odour
OL,14,Fannoyance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1783711192
OL,3,CPeople asked to share views on
OL,4,Clandfill odour stench
OL,6,F"Individuals can react differently to
OL,7,Fhydrogen sulphide (H2S) odour, and
OL,8,Fsome people may be more sensitive to
OL,9,Fit than others. People living near the
OL,10,Fsite may experience temporary symptoms
OL,11,Fincluding headaches, nausea,
OL,12,Fdizziness, watery eyes, a stuffy nose,
OL,13,Fan irritated throat and coughing.
OL,14,FThose with pre-existing respiratory
OL,15,Fconditions may be particularly
OL,16,Faffected, and some residents may also
OL,17,Fexperience sleep disruption and stress.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
